        "action": "Reconsider and accept MPs' proposals to clean up the fashion industry",
        "additional_details": "\"Fixing Fashion: clothing consumption and sustainability\", Environmental Audit Committee (19 February 2019). See \"Conclusion and recommendations\"\r\nhttps://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm201719/cmselect/cmenvaud/1952/full-report.html#heading-11\r\n\r\n\"Ministers reject fast fashion impact advice\", BBC (18 June 2019) https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-48667641",
